_Hispa’el_ Future Tense: The [[{{_hispa’el_}} binyan]] has a [[future tense]], which is one of the [[_Hispa’el_ tenses|“tenses” of the _hispa’el_ binyan]].
- The _hispa’el_ future tense has [[_Hispa’el_ Future Tense for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _hispa’el_ future tense has conjugations for irregular shorushim that will be added at a later time.
